      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Secretary Moore of the chamber\nof commerce is in receipt of letter\nfrom w. ID. Rhodes of Kalispell,\nMont. stating that they are very\nanxious to secure an aeroplane for\nuse at the coming county fair, Oc-\ntober lila. 1t leaks out that Mr..\nE. j. Arnold is arranging for an\naeroplane meet, to be held in Spo-\nkane, and that Mr.. Curtiss has been\ngiving exhibitions on these grounds\nalready. Mr.. Rhodes asks the cham\nDer Of commerce to put him in touch\nwith some one who will contract for\nthis splendid attraction."
    }
